Package owl.run.parser

Class PartialConfigurationParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • owl.run.parser.PartialConfigurationParser

  • public final class PartialConfigurationParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class used to parse a simplified command line (single exposed module with rest of the pipeline preconfigured). Additionally, multiple modes can be specified, which are selected through a special --mode switch.
